    "Early Netherlandish painting was to become one of his main fields of specialization.": [],
    "He held the stylistic approach of <a href=\"/friedlanderm\">Max J. Friedl\u00e4nder</a> in high esteem.": [],
    "In 1937, Boon started working in the Amsterdam Rijksmuseum as a volunteer and soon he became an assistant to the keeper of the drawings in the Print Room, M. D. Henkel (1879-1944).": [
